## Cron Setup (External Cron — NOT Vercel Crons)

The app uses **external cron-jobs** (e.g. cron-job.org), not Vercel's built-in crons.

Call these URLs with header `X-Cron-Secret: <CRON_SECRET>`:

| Endpoint | Recommended interval | What it does |
|----------|---------------------|--------------|
| `/api/cron/sync-platform-data` | Every 15–30 min | Account overview + post discovery + post metrics for all connected accounts |
| `/api/cron/metric-snapshots` | Daily | Follower/fan count daily snapshot (Instagram + Facebook) |
| `/api/cron/comment-automation` | Every 1–5 min | Comment replies automation |
| `/api/cron/process-scheduled` | Every 1–2 min | Publish scheduled posts |

