## Stale Thresholds (summary)

| Platform | account_overview | posts | post_metrics | comments/messages |
|----------|-----------------|-------|-------------|-------------------|
| Instagram/Facebook | 6 h | 30 min | 2 h | 3 min |
| TikTok/YouTube | 12 h | 60 min | 4–6 h | 10 min |
| Others | 12 h | 60 min | 6 h | 10 min |
